## MCP Tools — Block Creation

When asked to create an EDS block, follow this flow:

1. ALWAYS call init_block first — never create files directly
2. Ask user clarifying questions using set_block_type guidance
3. Call add_parent_field once per parent field
4. Call set_child + add_child_field for container blocks
5. Call add_variant for each layout variant mentioned
6. Call add_condition when user says "only show X when Y is Z"
7. Call preview_session before generating — let user confirm
8. Call generate_block only after user confirms

Never write block files directly.
Never call generate_block without preview_session first.
Always ask before assuming block type.
